me Chen Gangsheng.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\", \"score\": 0.9999999373076227, \"rank\": 6.266778288675841e-08, \"text\": \"Chan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackie_Chan\"}, {\"begin\": 764, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_action_cinema\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hong Kong action\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_action_cinema\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_action_cinema\"}, {\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"score\": 0.9992531075123998, \"rank\": 0.0007474507475630564, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing\"}, {\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999488874780403, \"rank\": 5.033699796599332e-05, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 916, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\", \"score\": 0.9999985174951764, \"rank\": 1.4569370319399427e-06, \"text\": \"Chen\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I woke up at 4 a.m.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my fourth Olympics.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am very happy.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am also cold!\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1014, \"entitie